4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge seeking to become cybersecurity specialists. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 students per class. Students will learn foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security and penetration testing. The bootcamp emphasizes risk management and compliance with standards such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4geeksacademy.com](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop